AI-Based Farmer Query Support and Advisory System

Project Title

AI-Based Farmer Query Support and Advisory System

---

Problem Statement

Farmers often face difficulties in obtaining timely and accurate information regarding crop diseases, weather conditions, fertilizer usage, pest control, and market prices. Due to limited access to agricultural experts, farmers may make incorrect decisions that affect crop yield and income. This project aims to provide an AI-powered platform where farmers can submit their queries and receive instant agricultural advice and recommendations.

---

Project Objectives

Primary Objectives

1. To provide instant agricultural guidance using Artificial Intelligence.
2. To assist farmers in making informed decisions related to crop management.
3. To reduce dependency on physical agricultural consultations.
4. To improve crop productivity and farming efficiency.

Secondary Objectives

1. To provide weather-based farming recommendations.
2. To offer crop disease identification and solutions.
3. To suggest suitable fertilizers and pesticides.
4. To provide market price information for agricultural products.
5. To support multilingual communication for farmers.

---

Module List

Module ID| Module Name| Description
M1| User Registration & Login| Farmers can create accounts and securely log in.
M2| Query Submission| Farmers can submit agriculture-related questions.
M3| AI Advisory Engine| AI processes queries and generates recommendations.
M4| Crop Disease Detection| Identifies crop diseases and provides remedies.
M5| Weather Information Module| Displays weather forecasts and farming suggestions.
M6| Fertilizer Recommendation| Suggests fertilizers based on crop type and soil conditions.
M7| Market Price Module| Provides current market prices for crops.
M8| Admin Dashboard| Manages users, queries, and system monitoring.

---

Database Tables

Table Name| Purpose
Users| Stores farmer account details.
Queries| Stores farmer questions and requests.
Responses| Stores AI-generated advisory responses.
Crops| Stores crop-related information.
Diseases| Stores crop disease details and remedies.
Weather| Stores weather forecast information.
Market_Prices| Stores crop market prices.
Admin| Stores administrator information.

