Expected Outcome

The AI-Based Farmer Query Support and Advisory System will provide farmers with quick and accurate agricultural guidance. The system will help farmers improve crop yield, reduce losses caused by diseases and pests, make better farming decisions, and access agricultural information anytime and anywhere through a user-friendly platform.

---

Future Enhancements

1. Voice-based query support.
2. Regional language support.
3. Mobile application development.
4. Integration with IoT-based smart farming devices.
5. Advanced image-based crop disease detection using Deep Learning.

---

Conclusion

The AI-Based Farmer Query Support and Advisory System is designed to bridge the gap between farmers and agricultural experts by providing AI-driven support and recommendations. The system promotes smart farming practices, improves productivity, and contributes to the overall development of the agricultural sector.
